         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a6"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>157</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>105</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1994c"/><citedRange>385</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:kolver1965"/><citedRange>83, 139</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... durch die ... Stimme [und] durch die Berührung mit dem Glanz [wtl. des Strahls] eingeladen, versammelten sie sich in dem Kloster Ṛṣipatana.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">... invited by the ... voice [and] by the touch of the ray, they gathered in the monastery Ṛṣipatana.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>83, 305</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a7"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>105</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1968"/><citedRange>207</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1994c"/><citedRange>385</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a8"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>105</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1997"/><citedRange>71</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1994c"/><citedRange>386</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:kolver1965"/><citedRange>82</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b1"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>144</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1994c"/><citedRange>387</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1994c"/><citedRange>388</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... the effort of sixty [and] forty Kalpas ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1994c"/><citedRange>388</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp