         </div>
         <div type="comments">
            <p><note type="parallels">MaitrHami 4, 6-8</note><note type="philcomment">This fragment contains part of the fourth act of the Maitreyasamitināṭaka; an Uy. parallel is MaitrHami 4, 6b22-8a1. See also <bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1999"/><citedRange>197-198</citedRange></bibl>.</note><note type="philcomment"><bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1994c"/><citedRange>384f</citedRange></bibl>.</note><note type="remarks">Fragment of a manuscript which includes A 251 - A 294 (cf. <bibl><title corresp="ref:gengetal2004a"/><citedRange>64-65</citedRange></bibl>).</note></p>
